Package com.heidiaandahl.controller

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddStory
    A servlet that adds a user's financial story and hides prior stories associated with the user.
    ApplicationStartup
    Initializer for the Income Experiences application.
    DisplayProfile
    A servlet that displays the profile of the current user for the session.
    EditStory
    A servlet that makes a user's prior story available as a starting point when they want to edit their story.
    FlagContent
    A servlet that marks a financial story "unsuitable" based on user input.
    LogIn
    The purpose of this servlet is to trigger authentication.
    LogOut
    A servlet that logs the user out by invalidating their session.
    Redirector
    A servlet that redirects the user to the home page.
    SearchStats
    A servlet that coordinates the search for survey and story data based on criteria chosen by the user.
    SearchTopics
    A servlet that gets financial stories based on a user's search terms and coordinates their display back to the user.
    SignUp
    A servlet that signs a new user up.
    TransferChartData
    Makes data from the session available for charts made using JavaScript.
